1. As the person in charge of data products in the growth and marketing group, lead the team to build the operation structure of data products, provide data services, promote the growth of performance and the innovation and optimization of functions, and improve efficiency;
2. In-depth understanding of products and user demands, making plans and optimization Suggestions according to business needs;
3. Improve the efficiency and organizational efficiency of the data team, conduct effect monitoring, and cooperate with the operation to make reasonable operation plans and strategies;
